text.tspan: Pin-to-pin connection is not shown intentionally
as the pins are overlapped with RPi header #1~#10.
Note that R2 and R3 has been removed
as TMP117 already has two 2.2K pull-up registers,
one for SDA, and the other for SCL.
JDVcc is separately connected to the relay board's JDVcc.
